Package energy.usef.core.workflow.dto

This package contains classes describing Data Transfer Objects (DTO), which are used to convey information to Pluggable Business Components.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectionMeterDataDto
    DTO class to carry information related to smart meter data on connection level (or per aggregator).
    ConnectionMeterEventDto
    DTO object for the ConnectionMeterEvent xml entity.
    FlexOfferDto
    Data Transfer Object for a FlexOffer.
    FlexOrderDto
    Data Transfer Object for a FlexOrder.
    FlexOrderSettlementDto
    DTO class for the settlement of one Flex Order.
    FlexRequestDto
    Data Transfer Object for a FlexRequest.
    MeterDataDto
    DTO class to carry information about smart meter data per period.
    MeterDataSetDto
    DTO class to carry information coming from the MDC participant.
    PrognosisDto
    DTO for the D-Prognosis Input Data.
    PtuFlexOfferDto
    Data Transfer Object conveying the PTU values for a FlexOfferDto.
    PtuFlexOrderDto
    Data Transfer Object to convey information related to the PTU of a FlexOrderDto.
    PtuFlexRequestDto
    Data Transfer Object conveying the PTU values for a FlexRequest.
    PtuMeterDataDto
    DTO class to carry information about smart meter data for 1 PTU.
    PtuPrognosisDto
    Data Transfer Object conveying the PTU values for a Prognosis.
    PtuSettlementDto
    DTO class containing the information of the settlement of a Flex Order for 1 PTU.
    SettlementDto
    DTO class which contains the list FlexOrderSettlementDto for an given interval of time defined by two dates.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AcknowledgementStatusDto
    Data Transfer Object for the AcknowledgementStatus.
    DispositionAcceptedDisputedDto
    DTO enumeration of the disposition accepted/disputed.
    DispositionTypeDto
    An enumeration to represent the disposition type.
    MeterDataQueryTypeDto
    DTO enumeration for the MeterDataQueryType.
    MeterEventTypeDto
    DTO enumeration for the MeterEventType.
    PrognosisTypeDto
    Enumeration of the different types of Prognosis in a Data Transfer Object.
    USEFRoleDto
    Enumeration of the different USEF roles in a Data Transfer Object.

Package energy.usef.core.workflow.dto Description

This package contains classes describing Data Transfer Objects (DTO), which are used to convey information to Pluggable Business Components.
